{"pageProps":{"entry":{"id":"local-singapore-why-it-works","title":"Why Singapore Works (For Me)","date":"2026-02-10","slug":"singapore-why-it-works","categories":["Adventure","Work"],"mood":"Reflective","summary":"SV gave me scale. Taiwan gave me roots. Singapore gave me perspective. This is what the city actually does to you.","wordCount":515,"location":"Singapore","source":"local","mdxSources":{"en":{"compiledSource":"var c=Object.defineProperty,d=Object.defineProperties;var g=Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptors;var p=Object.getOwnPropertySymbols;var i=Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty,r=Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable;var s=(e,t,n)=>t in e?c(e,t,{enumerable:!0,configurable:!0,writable:!0,value:n}):e[t]=n,o=(e,t)=>{for(var n in t||(t={}))i.call(t,n)&&s(e,n,t[n]);if(p)for(var n of p(t))r.call(t,n)&&s(e,n,t[n]);return e},h=(e,t)=>d(e,g(t));var l=(e,t)=>{var n={};for(var a in e)i.call(e,a)&&t.indexOf(a)<0&&(n[a]=e[a]);if(e!=null&&p)for(var a of p(e))t.indexOf(a)<0&&r.call(e,a)&&(n[a]=e[a]);return n};const layoutProps={},MDXLayout=\"wrapper\";function MDXContent(n){var a=n,{components:e}=a,t=l(a,[\"components\"]);return mdx(MDXLayout,h(o(o({},layoutProps),t),{components:e,mdxType:\"MDXLayout\"}),mdx(\"h1\",null,\"Why Singapore Works (For Me)\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I want to write an honest account of Singapore, not a tourism pitch or an expat's lament.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"This is neither.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"This is about timing.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"What I expected\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I expected a clean, efficient, slightly sterile city.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`A place that worked, but didn\\u2019t necessarily feel alive.\nA tech hub trying to replicate something that already existed elsewhere.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I was wrong in a more interesting way.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"What I got\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Singapore doesn\\u2019t try to be Silicon Valley.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It doesn\\u2019t need to.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It runs on a different model \\u2014 less mythology, more execution. Less narrative, more structure.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"And for where I was in my life, that mattered.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Because I didn\\u2019t need inspiration.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I needed stability.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"The January Loop\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"In January 2026, I went back to Silicon Valley for a short trip.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Stayed at my aunt\\u2019s place.\nSame streets. Same grocery stores. Same air.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Nothing had changed.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Which made it clear that something had.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I wasn\\u2019t looking at the Valley the same way anymore.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`The urgency was gone.\nThe need to prove something \\u2014 quieter.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"During that trip, I interviewed with a new company.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Not as a reach.\nNot as a \\u201Cmaybe I\\u2019ll get lucky.\\u201D`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Just\\u2026 a conversation.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"A few rounds later, I signed.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"What Changed\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"If this had happened a year earlier, it would have meant something different.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Validation.\nReturn.\nContinuation of a path that got interrupted.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"But this time, it didn\\u2019t feel like going back.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It felt like choosing from a different place.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Singapore created that distance.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Not just geographically \\u2014 but mentally.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"What Singapore Actually Does\"),mdx(\"p\",null,mdx(\"strong\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"It removes noise.\")),mdx(\"p\",null,`There\\u2019s less signaling here. Less posturing.\nPeople are building things, but they\\u2019re not constantly narrating it.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"That changes how you think.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,mdx(\"strong\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"It forces routine.\")),mdx(\"p\",null,\"The city is structured. Predictable. Efficient.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`At first, that feels limiting.\nThen it becomes grounding.`),mdx(\"p\",null,`After the chaos of leaving the US in 40 days,\nthat structure matters more than I expected.`),mdx(\"p\",null,mdx(\"strong\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"It puts you in between worlds.\")),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Time zone, geography, culture \\u2014 everything sits between East and West.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"You start seeing trade-offs more clearly.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"And once you see them, you can\\u2019t unsee them.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"What Doesn\\u2019t Work\"),mdx(\"p\",null,mdx(\"strong\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"The heat.\"),\" Still not negotiable.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,mdx(\"strong\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"The visa structure.\"),\" Clear, but always present in the background.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,mdx(\"strong\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"The emotional distance.\"),\" It takes time to build real connections here. Longer than I expected.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"The Contract\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Signing the new offer didn\\u2019t feel like a climax.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"No big moment. No sense of arrival.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Just a quiet confirmation:\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I\\u2019m still moving forward.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"But not in the same way as before.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`Less urgency.\nLess dependency on external validation.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"More\\u2026 control.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"The Net\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I\\u2019m here until July.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Then I go back to Taiwan.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`This time, it\\u2019s not a forced move.\nNot a compressed timeline.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"It\\u2019s planned.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Intentional.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"That difference matters more than the destination.\"),mdx(\"hr\",null),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Singapore works for me not because it\\u2019s perfect.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`But because it came at the exact moment I needed a place\nthat didn\\u2019t demand anything from me\\u2014\nexcept that I figure out how I actually want to live.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"And for the first time in a while,\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I am.\"))}MDXContent.isMDXComponent=!0;\n","scope":{}},"zh":{